@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
### Simple Message Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hi, who are you?"
}

### Multi-turn Conversation Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "What is the capital of South Korea?" },
    { "role": "assistant", "content": "The capital of South Korea is Seoul." },
    { "role": "user", "content": "What is its most famous landmark?" }
  ]
}

### Error Case: Missing Fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wrong_field": "This should fail"
}

